gomodel:SYNGO_368  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Gephyrin at GABAergic postsynaptic density of mitral intrinsic profile receiving receiving to symmetric GABAergic inputs.\nPreembedding electron microscopic immunohistochemistry on the olfactory bulb of GFP-GAD67 expressing mice.. Experimental description: The generation of GAD67-eGFP ( neo) mice, which ex- press eGFP selectively in GABAergic neurons under the control of the endogenous GAD67 gene promoter, has been described previously (Tamamaki et al., 2003). P. 15040" ;
